Rift Valley fever, Nigeria
--------------------------
Information received [and dated] 24 Jul 2017 from Dr Gideon Mbursa Mshelbwala, Director, Veterinary Services, Federal Ministry of Agriculture and Rural Development, ABUJA, Nigeria

